# Monorepo root ignore

# Node
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.next/
**/out/
**/coverage/
**/.turbo/

# Env files
**/.env
**/.env.*.local

# Logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# OS / Editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/

# Windows: `nul` is a reserved device name; a mistaken `> nul` in the repo root can create this file and Git cannot index it.
/nul

